title: The Profit Season 1 720p
description:
1. Car Cash
Two feuding brothers who buy used cars for cash have watched their business dry up. Just weeks away from being forced to close their doors, they meet serial entrepreneur Marcus Lemonis.

2. Maarse Florists
Maarse Florists was once the premier flower shop in Southern California. But after the founder died, the business floundered. Marcus Lemonis believes he can put the bloom back on this rose.

3. Planet Popcorn
Planet Popcorn started as a humble little stand at a fairground. Today it's a multimillion-dollar business. Despite generating all that cash, Planet Popcorn still can't show a profit.

4. Eco-Me
Eco-Me is an all-natural cleaning supply company in trouble. Marcus Lemonis has a game plan to turn the company around, but will Eco-Me's stubborn owners embrace change before it's too late?

5. LA Dogworks
LA Dogworks was started up by an eccentric hothead who built a state-of-the-art dog care facility. But his volatile leadership resulted in terrible morale that threatens the entire business.

6. Mr. Green Tea
The Profit visits Mr. Green Tea, a family-run specialty ice cream company being torn apart by two competing visions. Can Marcus stop the bickering and take Mr. Green Tea to the next level?
